34 Maggārammaṇattika, Kusalattika
Maggārammaṇattika, Kusalattika
43.
136Namaggārammaṇaṃ nakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paccayā maggārammaṇo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
137Hetuyā pañcatiṃsa…pe…  avigate pañcatiṃsa. (Naakusalaṃ naabyākataṃ natthi.)
